rem Outside Record Shop
rem 8/17/2017

do Examine Shop
 [
  print People fill the shop as well as the district, running about preoccupied. But
  print this type of shop is rare, and you wonder how they stay open peddling such an
  print ancient technology.
 ]

do Enter Shop
 [
  ifflag have badge
   [
    print A lot of people are in the shop, but you manage to squeeze your way in.
    go Harakeyto Records
   |
    print The place is busy right now, you should come back when it thins out a bit.
   ]
 ]

do Walk North
 [
  print You walk north, ignoring the buildings you pass, finally stopping at the
  print arcade.
  go Arcade Entrance
 ]

do Walk South
 [
  print You continue down the street until you come to Ozaka, an all night parlor.
  go Outside Ozaka
 ]

